{"id":"hammedatha","term":"Hammedatha","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Father of Haman, designated usually “the Agagite” (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Esther 3:1\">Esther 3:1</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 1:10\">10</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 8:5\">8:5</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Esther 3:1","Genesis 1:10","Genesis 8:5"]}